1
00:01:32,740 --> 00:01:35,980
[Light to the Night]

2
00:01:58,960 --> 00:01:59,530
Use this.

3
00:02:01,390 --> 00:02:02,220
I checked.

4
00:02:02,640 --> 00:02:03,570
After you clean it with this,

5
00:02:03,570 --> 00:02:04,580
no one will notice.

6
00:02:06,340 --> 00:02:08,420
[Heavy-Duty Bleach]

7
00:02:31,580 --> 00:02:34,580
[Light to the Night]
[Episode 27]

8
00:02:52,390 --> 00:02:53,020
Sister,

9
00:02:55,870 --> 00:02:57,090
these three days,

10
00:02:58,920 --> 00:03:00,740
I'll act like nothing happened.

11
00:03:01,990 --> 00:03:03,370
I'll make everyone believe

12
00:03:04,360 --> 00:03:05,650
Xu Zhihong is still alive.

13
00:03:11,870 --> 00:03:12,810
After three days,

14
00:03:13,240 --> 00:03:14,940
I'll stage a disappearance.

15
00:03:16,670 --> 00:03:18,020
But I need your help.

16
00:03:18,320 --> 00:03:20,250
A dis... disappearance?

17
00:03:21,590 --> 00:03:22,620
You know about

18
00:03:23,520 --> 00:03:24,620
the cursed building

19
00:03:24,640 --> 00:03:26,020
rumor of Yuanlongli, right?

20
00:03:27,920 --> 00:03:29,810
I want to use that rumor

21
00:03:30,710 --> 00:03:32,220
to make everyone believe

22
00:03:33,360 --> 00:03:33,780
that I

23
00:03:34,960 --> 00:03:35,850
and Xu Zhihong

24
00:03:36,960 --> 00:03:37,970
were both taken

25
00:03:37,990 --> 00:03:38,970
by that building.

26
00:03:40,040 --> 00:03:41,220
Why do it this way?

27
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:44,410
Why not just leave quietly?

28
00:03:44,430 --> 00:03:45,300
Wouldn't that be easier?

29
00:03:48,870 --> 00:03:49,940
It's not that simple.

30
00:03:50,590 --> 00:03:51,940
I borrowed from loan sharks.

31
00:03:52,550 --> 00:03:54,090
And Song Qingsong

32
00:03:54,110 --> 00:03:55,690
from the cement factory was watching me.

33
00:03:57,080 --> 00:03:58,220
He made it clear

34
00:03:59,670 --> 00:04:01,300
he wants me gone from Weiyang.

35
00:04:01,760 --> 00:04:02,970
But that works out too.

36
00:04:04,670 --> 00:04:07,020
Even if the police find out

37
00:04:07,040 --> 00:04:08,780
we disappeared on purpose,

38
00:04:09,670 --> 00:04:11,020
we can still shift the blame

39
00:04:11,040 --> 00:04:12,650
onto Song Qingsong.

40
00:04:14,430 --> 00:04:15,530
At least they won't suspect

41
00:04:15,550 --> 00:04:16,740
Xu Zhihong's death.

42
00:04:18,390 --> 00:04:18,810
But...

43
00:04:19,960 --> 00:04:20,330
But...

44
00:04:21,150 --> 00:04:21,810
if you leave,

45
00:04:21,830 --> 00:04:23,130
what am I supposed to do?

46
00:04:24,880 --> 00:04:25,500
Sister,

47
00:04:26,440 --> 00:04:27,420
stay here for now.

48
00:04:28,790 --> 00:04:30,690
If Xu Zhihong and I disappear

49
00:04:30,710 --> 00:04:31,500
and then you leave too,

50
00:04:32,080 --> 00:04:32,770
the police will definitely

51
00:04:32,790 --> 00:04:34,210
suspect you.

52
00:04:34,830 --> 00:04:35,420
Besides,

53
00:04:35,440 --> 00:04:36,450
no one knows that

54
00:04:36,470 --> 00:04:37,540
we even know each other.

55
00:04:41,030 --> 00:04:42,250
How long do I stay?

56
00:04:43,520 --> 00:04:44,260
This place...

57
00:04:45,440 --> 00:04:45,770
I...

58
00:04:46,030 --> 00:04:47,010
I can't live here anymore.

59
00:04:53,520 --> 00:04:54,180
Sister,

60
00:04:55,080 --> 00:04:56,570
hold on until Yao Xincheng returns.

61
00:04:57,470 --> 00:04:58,620
He'll sell the house

62
00:04:59,270 --> 00:05:00,210
and give you the money.

63
00:05:00,680 --> 00:05:01,570
Otherwise, all the hardship

64
00:05:01,590 --> 00:05:02,500
will be for nothing.

65
00:05:11,080 --> 00:05:11,370
Then...

66
00:05:12,440 --> 00:05:13,330
what about you?

67
00:05:14,830 --> 00:05:15,740
Where will you go?

68
00:05:17,710 --> 00:05:18,130
I...

69
00:05:19,680 --> 00:05:20,890
I'll find a place

70
00:05:22,640 --> 00:05:23,940
where nobody

71
00:05:23,960 --> 00:05:25,330
knows who we are,

72
00:05:27,350 --> 00:05:28,890
and build a safe home.

73
00:05:30,080 --> 00:05:31,300
I'll wait for you there.

74
00:05:32,680 --> 00:05:33,250
Sister,

75
00:05:37,440 --> 00:05:38,060
no one can

76
00:05:38,080 --> 00:05:38,940
give us safety.

77
00:05:42,150 --> 00:05:43,570
We can only rely on ourselves.

78
00:05:53,080 --> 00:05:53,690
Don't be scared.

79
00:07:27,220 --> 00:07:30,020
[Yuanlongli International Garden]

80
00:08:35,200 --> 00:08:36,260
Xu Zhihong's body

81
00:08:36,280 --> 00:08:37,380
was disposed of in stages.

82
00:08:38,320 --> 00:08:39,610
Xu Meng kept the head and hands

83
00:08:39,630 --> 00:08:40,490
for last.

84
00:08:41,080 --> 00:08:42,970
When I impersonated Xu Zhihong,

85
00:08:42,990 --> 00:08:43,900
I needed his hand

86
00:08:43,920 --> 00:08:45,140
to press the elevator buttons

87
00:08:45,160 --> 00:08:46,090
and leave fingerprints.

88
00:08:47,510 --> 00:08:48,940
After it was done,

89
00:08:48,960 --> 00:08:50,020
I got a tool bag

90
00:08:50,040 --> 00:08:51,060
and packed them inside.

91
00:08:51,830 --> 00:08:52,850
Xu Meng disposed of them.

92
00:09:04,830 --> 00:09:05,850
Xu Meng finally left

93
00:09:05,870 --> 00:09:07,300
through the underground garage.

94
00:09:08,200 --> 00:09:09,570
That's the whole process.

95
00:09:11,200 --> 00:09:11,970
The elevator door

96
00:09:12,400 --> 00:09:13,630
and the garage key—

97
00:09:14,510 --> 00:09:15,140
where did they come from?

98
00:09:16,280 --> 00:09:17,300
The elevator key

99
00:09:17,320 --> 00:09:18,210
is universal.

100
00:09:19,040 --> 00:09:20,210
You can buy it at a hardware store.

101
00:09:21,400 --> 00:09:22,610
As for the garage key,

102
00:09:22,630 --> 00:09:23,780
Xu Meng already had one.

103
00:09:24,590 --> 00:09:25,940
She used to work at Pattia

104
00:09:26,960 --> 00:09:28,540
and always used the underground access.

105
00:09:30,510 --> 00:09:31,940
That's quite thorough planning.

106
00:09:33,160 --> 00:09:33,900
We thought

107
00:09:33,920 --> 00:09:35,260
the plan was solid too.

108
00:09:36,350 --> 00:09:37,940
But something still went wrong.

109
00:10:09,200 --> 00:10:09,730
Come on.

110
00:10:10,920 --> 00:10:11,610
Why are you hiding?

111
00:11:07,710 --> 00:11:08,060
Hello?

112
00:11:08,920 --> 00:11:09,610
It's me.

113
00:11:22,470 --> 00:11:23,330
I was spotted

114
00:11:23,350 --> 00:11:24,380
by Song Qingsong's driver.

115
00:11:25,400 --> 00:11:26,330
I'm locked up.

116
00:11:26,990 --> 00:11:28,020
Did he do anything to you?

117
00:11:28,590 --> 00:11:29,380
Don't worry.

118
00:11:30,630 --> 00:11:31,730
He can't do anything.

119
00:11:32,560 --> 00:11:33,940
He's just a sick pervert.

120
00:11:35,470 --> 00:11:36,210
I've figured out

121
00:11:36,230 --> 00:11:37,060
how to deal with him.

122
00:11:39,440 --> 00:11:39,900
By the way,

123
00:11:40,560 --> 00:11:41,490
that tool bag—

124
00:11:42,230 --> 00:11:43,140
What about it?

125
00:11:45,080 --> 00:11:45,490
It's nothing.

126
00:11:47,200 --> 00:11:48,090
I already burned it.

127
00:11:51,350 --> 00:11:51,690
I'm

128
00:11:51,990 --> 00:11:53,420
doing what you said—

129
00:11:53,440 --> 00:11:55,160
writing the rhyme on flyers.

130
00:11:55,350 --> 00:11:56,810
I'll hand them out tomorrow.

131
00:11:57,200 --> 00:11:58,260
Don't wait till tomorrow.

132
00:11:58,990 --> 00:11:59,900
Go now.

133
00:12:01,110 --> 00:12:02,450
Everyone's watching

134
00:12:02,470 --> 00:12:03,380
the comeback livestream.

135
00:12:04,400 --> 00:12:05,570
The streets will be empty.

136
00:12:06,920 --> 00:12:07,330
Also,

137
00:12:07,870 --> 00:12:08,730
that dress you gave me—

138
00:12:08,750 --> 00:12:09,810
the Bowls one—

139
00:12:09,830 --> 00:12:10,730
I forgot to take it.

140
00:12:11,710 --> 00:12:12,780
It can be traced back to Yao Xincheng's

141
00:12:12,800 --> 00:12:13,780
purchase record.

142
00:12:14,230 --> 00:12:15,140
We need to erase it.

143
00:12:15,710 --> 00:12:16,210
Okay.

144
00:12:17,400 --> 00:12:18,920
The police were in Yuanlongli all day

145
00:12:18,920 --> 00:12:19,970
investigating the disappearance.

146
00:12:19,990 --> 00:12:22,140
I'm worried the place

147
00:12:22,160 --> 00:12:23,300
where we buried it

148
00:12:23,320 --> 00:12:24,490
might not be safe.

149
00:12:25,160 --> 00:12:26,610
I'll find a way to get out tomorrow,

150
00:12:27,440 --> 00:12:28,420
dig it up,

151
00:12:28,440 --> 00:12:29,330
and burn it.

152
00:12:29,990 --> 00:12:31,180
Even if it's found,

153
00:12:31,630 --> 00:12:32,940
they won't identify the body.

154
00:12:33,960 --> 00:12:34,730
I'll go instead.

155
00:12:38,400 --> 00:12:39,380
Just keep yourself safe.

156
00:12:50,080 --> 00:12:50,900
The next day

157
00:12:52,040 --> 00:12:53,490
I went to where the body was buried,

158
00:12:55,470 --> 00:12:56,900
dug it up,

159
00:12:56,920 --> 00:12:58,260
and burned it

160
00:12:58,280 --> 00:12:59,490
along with the blue heels.

161
00:12:59,870 --> 00:13:00,730
Then buried it again.

162
00:13:02,080 --> 00:13:03,330
I was covered in dirt,

163
00:13:04,350 --> 00:13:05,490
afraid the police might see me,

164
00:13:06,750 --> 00:13:08,450
so I bought a potted plant

165
00:13:09,830 --> 00:13:11,850
to make it look like the dirt came from that.

166
00:13:14,590 --> 00:13:15,380
Turns out...

167
00:13:17,590 --> 00:13:17,940
Watch out.

168
00:13:33,960 --> 00:13:35,570
Maybe it's because

169
00:13:35,870 --> 00:13:37,610
I've been on edge for too long...

170
00:13:42,230 --> 00:13:43,020
How about

171
00:13:43,040 --> 00:13:44,330
you come in and wash up?

172
00:13:47,440 --> 00:13:48,490
I kept worrying the police

173
00:13:48,510 --> 00:13:49,570
would show up at my door.

174
00:13:51,560 --> 00:13:53,420
But when I saw Ran that time,

175
00:13:54,750 --> 00:13:55,610
I felt like

176
00:13:56,630 --> 00:13:57,540
the police weren't

177
00:13:57,560 --> 00:13:58,490
that scary after all.

178
00:13:59,870 --> 00:14:01,730
So I thought I'd let him come in and take a look.

179
00:14:03,200 --> 00:14:04,020
Once he saw,

180
00:14:06,590 --> 00:14:07,450
maybe after that

181
00:14:07,470 --> 00:14:08,540
I wouldn't be so nervous anymore.

182
00:14:23,510 --> 00:14:24,450
This photo—

183
00:14:24,470 --> 00:14:25,380
what's going on?

184
00:14:30,110 --> 00:14:30,940
It was Wu Shanlong

185
00:14:30,960 --> 00:14:32,140
who forced Xu Meng to take it.

186
00:14:49,990 --> 00:14:50,450
Get in.

187
00:14:51,560 --> 00:14:52,210
I'm not going.

188
00:14:55,040 --> 00:14:56,300
You think you've got

189
00:14:56,320 --> 00:14:57,570
other options right now?

190
00:14:58,230 --> 00:14:59,420
I tell you to do something,

191
00:14:59,440 --> 00:15:00,180
you do it.

192
00:15:02,160 --> 00:15:02,810
Wu Shanlong,

193
00:15:03,510 --> 00:15:04,180
aren't you afraid

194
00:15:04,200 --> 00:15:05,810
of keeping me around,

195
00:15:06,200 --> 00:15:07,970
one day I might slip

196
00:15:08,320 --> 00:15:10,020
and expose how you scammed

197
00:15:10,040 --> 00:15:10,630
Song Qingsong?

198
00:15:10,630 --> 00:15:11,810
You—

199
00:15:13,920 --> 00:15:14,940
Try it.

200
00:15:15,200 --> 00:15:16,730
I'll kill you right now.

201
00:15:17,230 --> 00:15:18,300
Then go ahead.

202
00:15:18,870 --> 00:15:19,970
I already told

203
00:15:19,990 --> 00:15:21,260
my dad everything about you.

204
00:15:21,630 --> 00:15:22,380
He's already

205
00:15:22,400 --> 00:15:23,140
left Weiyang.

206
00:15:23,680 --> 00:15:24,780
If I die,

207
00:15:25,630 --> 00:15:26,610
what do you think he'll do?

208
00:15:33,510 --> 00:15:35,490
Xu Meng couldn't reveal herself,

209
00:15:36,200 --> 00:15:37,540
so she kept moving around

210
00:15:37,560 --> 00:15:38,380
doing under-the-table jobs.

211
00:15:39,560 --> 00:15:40,450
During that time,

212
00:15:41,400 --> 00:15:42,690
we barely stayed in touch.

213
00:15:44,230 --> 00:15:46,140
Until the spring of 2002,

214
00:15:47,830 --> 00:15:49,140
she suddenly called me.

215
00:15:50,470 --> 00:15:51,900
Said she'd saved enough money

216
00:15:53,470 --> 00:15:54,300
and wanted

217
00:15:54,320 --> 00:15:55,570
to go back to where we first met

218
00:15:59,440 --> 00:16:00,900
and build a small house.

219
00:16:02,320 --> 00:16:03,540
I was so excited.

220
00:16:04,080 --> 00:16:05,210
I immediately called

221
00:16:05,230 --> 00:16:06,140
Yao Xincheng

222
00:16:06,630 --> 00:16:08,090
to ask when he'd be back.

223
00:16:09,160 --> 00:16:10,210
Yao Xincheng said

224
00:16:10,750 --> 00:16:12,210
he planned to return by year's end.

225
00:16:13,460 --> 00:16:14,540
When that happens,

226
00:16:14,710 --> 00:16:15,690
he'll keep his promise,

227
00:16:16,110 --> 00:16:17,090
sell the house,

228
00:16:17,990 --> 00:16:18,850
and give me the money.

229
00:16:19,990 --> 00:16:21,180
Hearing that,

230
00:16:23,230 --> 00:16:24,140
we got so excited

231
00:16:24,160 --> 00:16:25,090
stayed on the phone

232
00:16:25,800 --> 00:16:27,260
all night long.

233
00:16:30,400 --> 00:16:31,570
Back then, it felt like

234
00:16:33,590 --> 00:16:34,570
hope

235
00:16:36,710 --> 00:16:38,140
was finally within reach.

236
00:16:50,680 --> 00:16:51,690
But not long after,

237
00:16:53,400 --> 00:16:54,380
something happened.

238
00:17:01,440 --> 00:17:02,020
Hi there,

239
00:17:02,680 --> 00:17:03,490
I'm from property management.

240
00:17:03,800 --> 00:17:05,620
I'm here to check the TV lines.

241
00:17:05,640 --> 00:17:06,530
Lately people

242
00:17:06,550 --> 00:17:07,580
have been complaining

243
00:17:07,600 --> 00:17:08,290
about poor signal.

244
00:17:10,270 --> 00:17:10,820
You—

245
00:17:11,600 --> 00:17:12,050
You're from

246
00:17:12,070 --> 00:17:12,730
property management?

247
00:17:13,310 --> 00:17:14,580
I just

248
00:17:14,600 --> 00:17:15,410
[Yuanlongli International Garden Property]
started last week.

249
00:17:18,960 --> 00:17:19,820
Hey,

250
00:17:19,840 --> 00:17:20,970
have we met before?

251
00:17:23,030 --> 00:17:23,340
Well—

252
00:17:35,470 --> 00:17:36,940
I'd seen Wu Shanlong before

253
00:17:36,960 --> 00:17:37,820
at Qihuang Clinic,

254
00:17:39,400 --> 00:17:40,490
but he didn't recognize me.

255
00:17:47,120 --> 00:17:47,620
Alright,

256
00:17:47,640 --> 00:17:48,420
the lines are fine.

257
00:17:50,550 --> 00:17:51,490
I'll head to the next place.

258
00:17:54,840 --> 00:17:55,580
Thanks.

259
00:18:26,990 --> 00:18:28,140
I wanted to call the police,

260
00:18:29,400 --> 00:18:30,140
but I was afraid

261
00:18:30,160 --> 00:18:31,380
if Wu Shanlong got arrested,

262
00:18:32,270 --> 00:18:34,010
he'd expose Xu Meng.

263
00:18:34,530 --> 00:18:35,940
So I held it in.

264
00:18:36,560 --> 00:18:38,180
I kept the windows shut

265
00:18:39,440 --> 00:18:40,470
and the curtains closed every day.

266
00:18:46,360 --> 00:18:47,140
After finally getting

267
00:18:47,160 --> 00:18:48,450
a few years of sunlight,

268
00:18:51,990 --> 00:18:53,210
I had to block it out again.

269
00:18:54,640 --> 00:18:55,890
So Wu Shanlong

270
00:18:56,600 --> 00:18:58,180
didn't know your connection to Xu Meng,

271
00:18:59,600 --> 00:19:00,530
and never threatened you?

272
00:19:04,510 --> 00:19:06,010
We approached him first.

273
00:19:08,750 --> 00:19:09,660
At that time,

274
00:19:10,270 --> 00:19:11,820
Xu Zhihong's head

275
00:19:12,270 --> 00:19:12,820
was

276
00:19:12,840 --> 00:19:14,050
found on the rooftop.

277
00:19:14,790 --> 00:19:15,820
I was so scared

278
00:19:15,840 --> 00:19:16,660
I couldn't sleep for days.

279
00:19:29,740 --> 00:19:32,100
[Reward Notice: 8,000 yuan for useful leads]

280
00:19:37,790 --> 00:19:38,490
Back then,

281
00:19:39,510 --> 00:19:41,580
Wu Shanlong ran into me in the garage.

282
00:19:42,710 --> 00:19:44,010
I had no choice.

283
00:19:44,880 --> 00:19:46,420
I had to hide the tool bag

284
00:19:46,440 --> 00:19:47,780
nearby.

285
00:19:49,600 --> 00:19:50,620
A few days later,

286
00:19:50,920 --> 00:19:52,420
when I went back for it,

287
00:19:56,640 --> 00:19:57,450
I realized

288
00:19:59,270 --> 00:20:00,050
it was gone.

289
00:20:04,030 --> 00:20:05,490
I didn't tell you

290
00:20:06,550 --> 00:20:07,860
because I didn't want you to worry.

291
00:20:10,270 --> 00:20:10,690
Meng,

292
00:20:13,390 --> 00:20:14,240
run.

293
00:20:16,310 --> 00:20:17,620
The farther, the better.

294
00:20:24,470 --> 00:20:25,050
Sister,

295
00:20:27,070 --> 00:20:28,450
I've been running for years.

296
00:20:30,990 --> 00:20:32,140
I don't want to run anymore.

297
00:20:34,640 --> 00:20:35,210
What if—

298
00:20:38,750 --> 00:20:40,340
what if the police find us?

299
00:20:40,360 --> 00:20:40,940
What do we do?

300
00:20:47,470 --> 00:20:48,210
There's someone

301
00:20:51,680 --> 00:20:53,100
who can die in our place.

302
00:20:55,750 --> 00:20:56,770
Xu Meng dug up

303
00:20:56,790 --> 00:20:58,180
