310
00:21:15,160 --> 00:21:16,210
The trap that killed

311
00:21:16,230 --> 00:21:16,900
Wu Shanlong—

312
00:21:17,470 --> 00:21:18,770
Xu Meng taught me how to make it.

313
00:21:19,990 --> 00:21:20,530
That day,

314
00:21:21,680 --> 00:21:22,620
