563
00:39:44,920 --> 00:39:45,970
Fire! Fire!

564
00:39:45,970 --> 00:39:48,030
[Carousel's Dead Heat]

565
00:39:48,030 --> 00:39:49,300
Fire! Fire!

566
00:39:49,510 --> 00:39:50,010
Call the police!

567
00:39:50,030 --> 00:39:51,340
Call the police!

568
00:39:51,360 --> 00:39:52,340
