575
00:40:16,590 --> 00:40:16,940
Xiaohe!

576
00:40:17,240 --> 00:40:17,610
Xiaohe!

577
00:40:18,150 --> 00:40:18,700
Sit down.

578
00:40:19,760 --> 00:40:20,420
Sit down.

579
00:40:22,880 --> 00:40:23,220
Sit down.

580
00:40:29,720 --> 00:40:30,340
