work.

600
00:41:35,440 --> 00:41:36,340
I still need my job.

601
00:41:38,280 --> 00:41:38,970
You must be thirsty.

602
00:41:38,990 --> 00:41:39,820
I'll get you some water.

603
00:41:52,190 --> 00:41:53,300
You're moving?

604
00:41:54,590 --> 00:41:55,340
Didn't you say

605
00:41:55,360 --> 00:41:56,820
you'd stay till it's sold?

606
00:41:59,990 --> 00:42:00,530
Well—

607
00:42:00,550 --> 00:42:02,170
this place leaks,

608
00:42:02,190 --> 00:42:03,970
and since we're selling it,

609
00:42:03,990 --> 00:42:05,010
I figured I'd move out first.

610
00:42:05,590 --> 00:42:07,130
Closer to work,

611
00:42:07,400 --> 00:42:08,490
save on commute.

612
00:42:09,960 --> 00:42:11,490
Then don't rent a place.

613
00:42:12,030 --> 00:42:12,860
Come with me.

614
00:42:13,240 --> 00:42:14,700
When Yao gets back,

615
00:42:14,720 --> 00:42:15,940
you can come back.

616
00:42:16,470 --> 00:42:17,700
You can find work

617
00:42:17,720 --> 00:42:18,940
anywhere, right?

618
00:42:22,630 --> 00:42:23,130
Meng,

619
00:42:24,670 --> 00:42:25,610
I think

620
00:42:25,630 --> 00:42:26,260
I should wait.

621
00:42:26,920 --> 00:42:27,780
Let's wait a bit longer.

622
00:42:28,920 --> 00:42:29,260
Okay?

623
00:42:33,070 --> 00:42:33,570
Sister,

624
00:42:35,320 --> 00:42:36,490
what are you waiting for?

625
00:42:37,360 --> 00:42:38,090
Is it this place—

626
00:42:38,880 --> 00:42:40,610
something here you can't leave?

627
00:42:42,360 --> 00:42:43,220
Or is it—

628
00:42:45,550 --> 00:42:47,130
someone you can't let go of?

629
00:42:49,590 --> 00:42:50,650
How could that be?

630
00:42:51,990 --> 00:42:52,650
I just—

631
00:42:52,670 --> 00:42:54,170
I already paid three months' rent.

632
00:42:54,190 --> 00:42:55,380
Leaving now

633
00:42:55,400 --> 00:42:56,260
would be a waste.

634
00:42:57,630 --> 00:42:58,860
I'm going to the restroom.

635
00:43:46,720 --> 00:43:48,010
For the next few days,

636
00:43:49,440 --> 00:43:50,900
I didn't leave Weiyang.

637
00:43:51,800 --> 00:43:53,010
I just wanted to find out

638
00:43:54,440 --> 00:43:56,170
who the man in those slippers

639
00:43:57,240 --> 00:43:58,570
really was.

640
00:44:02,580 --> 00:44:07,300
♪I hear a voice from the depths of the valley♪

641
00:44:08,300 --> 00:44:11,660
♪Tinged with madness♪

642
00:44:12,180 --> 00:44:15,500
♪And hysteria♪

643
00:44:17,420 --> 00:44:22,140
♪I see the familiar self in my dream♪

644
00:44:23,740 --> 00:44:27,100
♪So avoidant♪

645
00:44:27,620 --> 00:44:30,940
♪So distraught♪

646
00:44:32,580 --> 00:44:37,300
♪That was a faraway memory♪

647
00:44:38,900 --> 00:44:42,260
♪I'm praying♪

648
00:44:42,740 --> 00:44:46,100
♪For my fate♪

649
00:44:48,380 --> 00:44:53,020
♪That's a secret that only belongs to time♪

650
00:44:54,260 --> 00:44:57,620
♪It's only a secret♪

651
00:44:58,100 --> 00:45:01,460
♪If no one brings it up♪

652
00:45:02,700 --> 00:45:06,220
♪Who will complete the puzzle of this lie♪

653
00:45:06,660 --> 00:45:10,380
♪Line by line, whose name are they calling out?♪

654
00:45:10,500 --> 00:45:14,180
♪Nightfall is the finale of all answers♪

655
00:45:14,180 --> 00:45:17,860
♪Only belonging to this barren land♪

656
00:45:17,940 --> 00:45:21,820
♪Who came from the forsaken crowd?♪

657
00:45:21,980 --> 00:45:25,860
♪Caressing a rusted body♪

658
00:45:25,860 --> 00:45:29,700
♪Stashing the secret on a certain floor♪

659
00:45:29,700 --> 00:45:37,540
♪Without making any ripples♪

660
00:45:40,380 --> 00:45:46,020
♪Any ripples♪

661
00:45:46,500 --> 00:45:50,020
♪Who will complete the puzzle of this lie♪

662
00:45:50,500 --> 00:45:54,180
♪Line by line, whose name are they calling out?♪

663
00:45:54,260 --> 00:45:57,940
♪Nightfall is the finale of all answers♪

664
00:45:57,940 --> 00:46:01,660
♪Only belonging to this barren land♪

665
00:46:01,700 --> 00:46:05,620
♪Who came from the forsaken crowd?♪

666
00:46:05,780 --> 00:46:09,660
♪Caressing a rusted body♪

667
00:46:09,660 --> 00:46:13,500
♪Stashing the secret on a certain floor♪

668
00:46:13,500 --> 00:46:24,140
♪In the loneliness of nightfall♪
